  "title": "PROJECT ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p>­­­­<u><strong>PROJECT ENGINEER</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>We are looking for a Solar Project Engineer who is passionate about deploying solar energy in Singapore.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirement</strong></u></p><p>Design, build and install solar energy systems</p><p>Onsite planning and managing of installation teams</p><p>Contact point between the company and client during construction stage</p><p>Create and execute project work plans and revise as appropriate to meet changing needs and requirements.</p><p>Hands on implementation on site</p><p>Ensure smooth delivery of the project completion/SystemTurn On</p><p><strong>Skills and Competencies</strong></p><p>Excellent communicator who is able to work independently</p><p>Diploma/Degree in Electrical Engineering or related fields</p><p>4 Years of experience in Project Engineer (Solar)</p><p>Candidate with experience in solar project execution will be in advantage</p><p>Knowledge in software (PVsyst) & Autocad</p><p>A team player who is results and customer oriented, independent, creative and passionate about renewables</p>",
